snippet.title: BORING MAN OTSC - V2 Community Trailer
snippet.description:
Thank you very much to all players who helped in the development of this ❤
Wug for making the music, Durdge and Adonai in modding, Sharply in map making, the spascord moderators for their feedback, of course to Spasman for giving me this opportunity and to all the beautiful BMAN Community who keeps gaming 🙌

🡆Download on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/346120/
🡆Download on GameJolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/boring-man-online-tactical-stickman-combat/18422
🡆Join the Discord server: https://discord.gg/chtzQ4m
